                              campaign. Vader has an extremely aggressive strategy of using bonus options on all questions that are
                              related to finance.
                            </p>
                          </div>

                          <div class='testimonials-speech' id='testimonial2'>
                            <p>
                              Luke Skywalker, a marketing executive has been in the top 10 quizzers since the begining of the campaign.
                              His strategy is unique that he rarely uses any bonus options; he has a very high correct answer rate. Luke
                              is extremely passive in his quizzing style but has a very sharp memory that makes him a daunting rival in
                              the campaign.
                            </p>
                          </div>

                          <% if user_signed_in? %>
                          <div class='testimonials-speech' id='testimonial3'>
                            <p>
                              Check out your rank on our leaderboard and the scores of the top players. Work out a strategy to maximize
                              your score to win the weekly and Grand Prizes
                            </p>
                          </div>
                          <% else %>
                          <div class='testimonials-speech' id='testimonial3'>
                            <p>
                              Log in to know your rank and to check out the scores of the top players.
